fixes.name: Customers - Active
fixes.originalSql: SELECT ISNULL(COUNT(*), 0) as value FROM P21.dbo.customer WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE inactive_flag <> 'Y'
fixes.fixedSql: SELECT COUNT(*) as value FROM dbo.customer WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE delete_flag <> 'Y'

fixes.name: Customers - Inactive
fixes.originalSql: SELECT ISNULL(COUNT(*), 0) as value FROM P21.dbo.customer WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE inactive_flag = 'Y'
fixes.fixedSql: SELECT COUNT(*) as value FROM dbo.customer WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE delete_flag = 'Y'
